The @@biron-banded archway@@N opens onto the Eternal Vault's entry landing, the third ascending floor. The air changes immediately above the threshold: colder, drier, and carrying the distinct chemical signature of mummification preservation — natron and cedar and resins that have stabilized in this environment for millennia. @@yhieroglyphic inscriptions@@N above the arch name this level and list what it contains: the eternal resting places of the pyramid's secondary pharaoh-lords, the vault where the most powerful undead await those who intrude. Recall is possible from this landing.
~
