@@yA Dark Corridor@@N~
A connecting corridor cutting diagonally through the vault's interior, its walls undecorated except for a continuous @@Rred border@@N at floor level — the danger indicator color that appears on this floor more frequently than on those below. The darkness here is thorough, resisting the peripheral light of adjacent rooms, as though the corridor itself maintains an active darkness rather than a passive absence of light.
